race.comment: CEEKAY'S CHOICE (3) finally shed the maiden tag at Gatton last time out and will have derived a stack of confidence from that breakthrough victory. Gets the services of Jones in the irons from the inside marble and can go back-to-back without surprising. LANTAU ISLAND (1) is one from one around this circuit and strips fitter second-up from the spell. Gets the reliable Gollan/Maloney combination and should be going very close. VESPER LYND (6) is a last-start winner over this track and trip who gets in well at the weights with the 3kg claim. Top-three aspirations. OOHLALOUVRE (5) has placed five of seven over this sprint journey and may earn some minor money again. THE POOL BOY (2) rounds out the selections.
